<P><HI>Elementa Philo&s;ophica:</HI> Containing chiefly, <HI>NOETICA,</HI> Or THINGS relating to the Mind <HI>or</HI> Under&s;tanding: AND <HI>ETHICA,</HI> Or THINGS relating to the MORAL BEHAVIOUR.</P>
