<DIV1 TYPE="half title">
<PB REF="006859_0128_102AABFEB0A7CF80">
<P>A SHORT SYSTEM OF MORALS.</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="title page">
<PB REF="006859_0129_102AAC0040DEE680" MS="y">
<P><HI>ETHICA:</HI> Or the Fir&s;t PRINCIPLES of Moral Philo&s;ophy; And e&s;pecially that Part which is called <HI>ETHICS.</HI> In a CHAIN of nece&s;&s;ary CONSEQUENCES from certain FACTS.</P>
<Q><P>Remember this, and &s;hew your&s;elves Men.</P>
